  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Save Progress Tips:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game supports both auto-save and manual save. Auto-save occurs at the beginning of each in-game month after the settlement process and may lag slightly behind your actual gameplay progress. It is recommended to manually save frequently for better progress security.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the newly appointed God of Harvest, you will embark on a journey filled with culinary delights and thrilling adventures. Collect a variety of ingredients such as seafood, spices, and fruits, and set sail to discover distant islands. Trade with local residents, spread the joy of food, and improve the quality of your dishes. Manage resources, build your farming and trade networks, and create a kingdom of prosperity and delicious food. Join this culinary adventure and immerse yourself in the wonders of unique ingredients and flavor explorations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/731ae0487e97dd726ca42503ed2473be.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/731ae0487e97dd726ca42503ed2473be.webm?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/731ae0487e97dd726ca42503ed2473be.mp4?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ A Real-World Map! ※</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel the world and experience diverse cultures and landscapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/2a1db65cc36463400283e3bcabb1ca62.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/2a1db65cc36463400283e3bcabb1ca62.webm?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/2a1db65cc36463400283e3bcabb1ca62.mp4?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ Distinctive Local Cuisines! ※</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize the food culture of each city and region.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/28806d0936dca157d1d65b2b6a57c3b8.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/28806d0936dca157d1d65b2b6a57c3b8.webm?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/28806d0936dca157d1d65b2b6a57c3b8.mp4?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ A Rich Variety of Native Ingredients! ※</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Consult vast historical records to uncover the true history of ingredients!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/c0d30fee782857bd0b0813ca9b6a386e.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/c0d30fee782857bd0b0813ca9b6a386e.webm?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ A Unique God of Harvest Experience! ※</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How will a God of Harvest, without divine powers, spread the joy of food across the world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/2629cd0304c4f5d7619ba2f16111ca79.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/2629cd0304c4f5d7619ba2f16111ca79.webm?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/2629cd0304c4f5d7619ba2f16111ca79.mp4?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ A Tangible Health-Boosting Experience! ※</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Under your guidance, the people across the globe will grow healthier and stronger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/617f4b8c5dfc9e7b0da262a4309eddd4.webp?t=1737106804\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/617f4b8c5dfc9e7b0da262a4309eddd4.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=337 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join us now!</strong> Become the God of Harvest and embark on a journey full of challenges and delicious adventures! With your wisdom and effort, spread global food and health to every corner of the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
